title: Daytons Bluff One Bedroom
posting_body: ['1158 E. 5th St. Key Features', 'Property type: duplex', 'Year Built: 1900', 'Unit sq footage: 1,160', 'Laundry:', 'In unit, separate basement', 'Floor: 1 and 2, plus basement', 'Bedrooms: 1+ (lofted bedroom upstairs plus egress-window room in basement) 13x12', 'Kitchen: 12x11', 'Laundry/Basement: 12x12', 'Bedroom/basement: 9x14', 'Living room: 16x13', 'Bathroom: 1 full (1st floor)', 'Other: deck, ceiling fan, central air, forced air heat', 'Tenant Pays: Cable/internet, ⅓ of monthly electricity and gas (to owner)', 'Owner pays: Trash, water/sewer', 'Lease duration: 12 months, preference for longer-term', 'Deposit: $950', 'Pet policy: up to 1 cat OK, any additional animals (more cats, dogs, reptiles…) reviewed on case-by-case basis', 'Open to trade for maintenance', 'Located in vibrant Dayton’s Bluff, close to… Metropolitan State University, downtown St. Paul, State Capital, 3M, Ecolab, on the 63, 74 lines, close to 61, 54 lines.', 'Caydence Coffee, East Side YMCA, American Indian Magnet, Dayton’s Bluff library, Manana Pupuseria, Arirang Korean, La Patrona taco truck, Margaret Park, 3rd St., Indian Mounds Park, grocery stores - Mississippi Market Co-Op, Cub Foods, Aldi, White Bear Target.', 'A qualified tenant is someone who…can pay rent on time ($975 due on the 1st of the month, unless otherwise agreed, via cash or Venmo, late fees may apply), takes care of their space (inside and outside), and shares the same desire of maintaining a safe and beautiful home.', 'Selected applicant must provide proof of income via two recent paystubs and bank statements showing at least two months’ rent in savings.', 'Soonest available: August 15th.']
